  <h3>Blueprint, the feature tracking application</h3>
  
  <p>
    <img src="/@@/blueprint" align="left" />Blueprint is the Launchpad
    feature tracker. It is used to help projects plan their feature
    development and coordinate across distributed teams.
  </p>

