  <h3>Greenhouse, the code management system</h3>
  
  <p>
    <img src="/@@/greenhouse" align="left" />"Greenhouse" (alert, alert,
    working title in use :-)) is the name of the Launchpad application which
    keeps track of the source code for a particular object in Launchpad.
  </p>
  
  <table>
