  <h3>Soyuz, the distribution package management system</h3>
  
  <p>
    <img src="/@@/soyuz" align="left" />Soyuz is the Launchpad subsystem
    that keeps track of the packages in a distribution. It handles uploads,
    the checking of permissions and consistency, builds, and the publishing
    of these packages into an archive.
  </p>

